Explanation of changes:
- Removed `parallel=True` to avoid thread‐spawn overhead on small problems (n≈20).
- Swapped `prange` to `range` so loops run efficiently single‐threaded under Numba’s nopython mode.
- These adjustments should substantially reduce per‐call overhead for energy/gradient evaluations at small to moderate n, boosting the `riesz_energy_n20_s1` benchmark.
